Female. Body 2.24 times as long as greatest width; without body ornamentation. Pleotelson posterior margin weakly tri-lobed, medial lobe not reaching to lateral lobes; uropod rami well extended beyond pleotelson apex; exopod longer than endopod, lateral and mesial margins fringed with dense setae (
